job.title: C# Application for Automating Tasks in Google Sheets
job.description:
We are looking for a skilled C# developer to write an application that can automate various tasks in Google Sheets. The application should be able to perform actions such as creating new columns/rows, updating data in those columns/rows, and updating existing data and formulas. The ideal candidate should have experience with C# programming and be familiar with the Google Sheets API. Attention to detail and problem-solving skills are a must. 

Relevant skills:
- C# programming
- Google Sheets API
- Automation
- Data manipulation
